section.features
  .container
    .section-header
      h2 Features
      p Everything you need in a terminal client
    .features-grid
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon ⚡
        h3 All-in-One Client
        p Works as a terminal, file manager, and SSH/SFTP/FTP/Telnet/Serial port/RDP/VNC/Spice client in one app.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🔐
        h3 Secure Auth
        p Supports publicKey + password authentication, global and per-session proxy, and SSH tunneling.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 📁
        h3 Remote File Editing
        p Double-click to directly edit remote files via integrated SFTP file manager with drag and drop.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🖥️
        h3 Multi-tab Terminal
        p Multiple terminal sessions in tabs with split panes, quick input to one or all terminals.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🔥
        h3 Global Hotkey
        p Toggle window visibility with a global hotkey (default Ctrl+2), similar to Guake-style drop terminals.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🎨
        h3 Themes & Customization
        p UI/terminal themes, terminal background images, transparent windows on Mac and Windows.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🌐
        h3 Multi-language
        p 14+ languages via community translations. Contributions and fixes welcome.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🤖
        h3 AI Assistant
        p Integration with DeepSeek, OpenAI, and any AI API for command suggestions, script writing, and content explanation.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 🔗
        h3 MCP & Deep Links
        p MCP widget for AI assistants and external tools. Open connections via URLs like ssh://user@host:22.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon ☁️
        h3 Cloud Sync
        p Sync bookmarks, themes, and quick commands to GitHub/Gitee secret gists, WebDAV, or custom servers.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 📎
        h3 Zmodem & Trzsz
        p Supports Zmodem (rz/sz) and Trzsz (trz/tsz) file transfer, compatible with tmux.
      .feature-card
        .feature-icon 📦
        h3 Cross-platform
        p Windows 7+ (x64/ARM64), macOS 10.15+ (x64/arm64), Linux (x64/arm64/Loong64) including glibc 2.17+.
